# Code ownership and default reviewers
# Syntax: https://docs.github.com/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything
*       @your-org/engineering-leads

# Rust code
*.rs    @your-org/rust-reviewers
/src/   @your-org/rust-reviewers
/auth-service/ @your-org/rust-reviewers
/policy-service/ @your-org/rust-reviewers

# GitHub workflows
/.github/workflows/ @your-org/devops

# Helm charts and k8s manifests
/helm/  @your-org/platform
/k8s/   @your-org/platform

# Documentation
/docs/  @your-org/docs
*.md    @your-org/docs

# Security policies and supply-chain
SECURITY.md @your-org/security
supply-chain-security.yml @your-org/security
/.github/workflows/supply-chain-security.yml @your-org/security
